{"tid":2437648,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵北環綫料2034年完工　區議員憂空窗期東鐵更擠迫","createTime":"2021-03-08T03:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T04:44:09.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1de19f720556530189665dba328c1a6030b54fff","tid":2437648,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T03:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/8bad6517985f0e8889dff463217157c2/2020/12/ca00216d9c477bba375972b93ae2e907.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F8bad6517985f0e8889dff463217157c2%2F2020%2F12%2Fca00216d9c477bba375972b93ae2e907.jpg&h=f115e636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北區區議會討論北環綫工程。路政署鐵路拓展處總工程師楊漢輝指，連接古洞、新田、牛潭尾、凹頭及錦上路的北環綫，工程會分為兩期，預計最終2034年完工，造價620億元，通車後來往古洞至上水車程，由15分鐘減至3分鐘；來往古洞至錦上路車程，由60至80分鐘減至12分鐘。 <br />\n<br />\n多名議員關注古洞北發展區落成後至北環線通車前的空窗期，擔心新增的人流只會令東鐵綫更加擠迫，新民主同盟陳惠達指近日東鐵綫由12卡車轉用9卡車後，已經收到多宗居民投訴，批評到大圍站才出現的屯馬綫分流作用，對南下的北區大埔居民並無幫助。港鐵代表指，日後設計北環綫等安排時，會審視東鐵綫運作情況。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2382042&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058ojkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=5eba4c81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382042</a>"},{"pid":"bda5d80d8e94d303724e8c9c18b529f553d205ad","tid":2437648,"uid":361247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:04:02.000Z","msg":"巴士又減一半"},{"pid":"9822eeb7f801d2c27e7285fe08d8924de769e73a","tid":2437648,"uid":259777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:04:46.000Z","msg":"其實由錦上路出發可唔可以直達落馬洲，定係要喺古洞搭返轉頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98f3a9f9c0e1ca24ac7727b674da5345b0e0f2e","tid":2437648,"uid":288913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:05:15.000Z","msg":"On9 線"},{"pid":"45d7e11b1a609c2b54e0670d09bcaa30cff207fc","tid":2437